EmailTemplate.subject: Year 9, 2015 Subject Selection Evening - 12 August, 2014
EmailTemplate.textOnly:
Dear Parents and Guardians of Year 8 students,
You are especially invited to a Subject Selection Expo for the current Year 8 students and their parents! The session will be held initially in the Cathedral at 6:30pm and then in the Heath Centre, Level 5 of SAH on Tuesday night, August 12, concluding after 8:00pm.
The main aim of the night is for families to gather as much information as possible in considering the subject path into Stage 5, so we strongly recommend that you and your child attend together!
Tea and coffee and juice will be provided on the night.
Please confirm your attendance via email to Robyn Pedley rpedley@sac.nsw.edu.au
I look forward to seeing you there,
Bruce Perry Registrar/Mathematics Teacher
St Andrew's Cathedral School
Sydney Square, Sydney NSW 2000, Australia direct +61 2 9286 9507 mobile 0418 255 923 email BPerry@sacs.nsw.edu.au phone +61 2 9286 9500 fax +61 29286 9550
